title: GameHouse - Little Shop  Road Trip - Hidden Object - Requested [
description:
Little Shop - Road Trip


Set off on the road to fun with Little Shop - Road Trip, 
an all-new hidden object adventure from the creators of 
the popular Little Shop of Treasures series. Take a break 
from running your shops, hit the road, and search stunning 
scenes from Seattle to South Beach on your quest to collect 
rare and exclusive items for your Little Shops back home. 
Complete 16 challenging road trips and unlock new bonus 
rounds and Blitz modes. Featuring two great game modes, 
thousands of cleverly hidden objects, and miles and miles 
of family fun, Little Shop - Road Trip is an incredible 
journey of breath-taking sights. Grab the keys to success today!
